        "body": "Fixes #1732\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\n\r\n  - Add a General preference to refresh enabled providers whenever the menu opens.\r\n  - Persist the new setting with a default of off, preserving the existing stale/missing-only menu refresh behavior unless enabled.\r\n  - When enabled, refresh all background-work providers concurrently in the background interaction context while keeping OpenAI\r\n  dashboard refresh deferred until menu close.\r\n  - Add localized strings and status menu tests for enabled and disabled refresh-on-open behavior.\r\n\r\n  ## Testing\r\n\r\n  - `swift test --filter StatusMenuTests`\r\n  - `make check`\r\n  - `git diff --check`\r\n  - `make test`\r\n\r\n  ## Screenshots / GIFs\r\n\r\n  Not included. Visible UI change is a single Preferences > General toggle.",
